@startuml pchat_trust_levels
!theme plain
title Persistent Chat - Key Trust Level State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<verified>> #D4EDDA
    BackgroundColor<<manual>> #C3E6CB
    BackgroundColor<<unverified>> #FFF3CD
    BackgroundColor<<disputed>> #F8D7DA
}

state "Unverified\n(TOFU)" as unverified <<unverified>> {
    unverified : First key acceptance
    unverified : via key-exchange
    unverified : ---
    unverified : Trust-on-first-use
    unverified : Visual fingerprint shown
}

state "Verified" as verified <<verified>> {
    verified : Multi-confirmation consensus
    verified : (FULL_ARCHIVE) or
    verified : key custodian trust shortcut
    verified : (POST_JOIN)
    verified : ---
    verified : Sufficient independent
    verified : peers confirmed same key
}

state "Manually Verified" as manual <<manual>> {
    manual : Out-of-band verification
    manual : completed by user
    manual : ---
    manual : Emoji / word-list /
    manual : hex fingerprint match
    manual : confirmed in person
}

state "Disputed" as disputed <<disputed>> {
    disputed : Conflicting key received
    disputed : from same peer
    disputed : ---
    disputed : User warned, must
    disputed : resolve manually or
    disputed : via key custodian
}

[*] --> unverified : First key-exchange\nreceived (TOFU)

unverified --> verified : Multi-confirmation\nconsensus reached\n(FULL_ARCHIVE)

unverified --> verified : Key custodian\ntrust shortcut\n(POST_JOIN)

unverified --> verified : Creator\ncountersignature\nvalidated

unverified --> manual : User completes\nOOB fingerprint\nverification

unverified --> disputed : Different key\nreceived from\nsame cert_hash

verified --> manual : User completes\nOOB fingerprint\nverification

verified --> disputed : Unexpected key\nchange detected

manual --> disputed : Unexpected key\nchange detected

disputed --> unverified : User accepts\nnew key\n(trust reset)

disputed --> verified : Key custodian\ncountersignature\nvalidates new key

disputed --> manual : User re-verifies\nOOB with new key

note right of disputed
  **Disputed Resolution**:
  1. Key custodian countersig validates
     new epoch -> auto-promote to Verified
  2. User manually accepts -> reset to
     Unverified (TOFU restart)
  3. User verifies OOB -> Manually Verified
  
  Channel is NOT hard-locked during
  dispute. Messages continue with
  a visible warning banner.
end note

note left of unverified
  **TOFU (Trust On First Use)**:
  The first key seen from a peer
  is accepted with a visual
  fingerprint displayed for
  optional OOB verification.
  
  Visual fingerprint formats:
  - 8 emoji sequence
  - 6 word list
  - Hex string
end note

note bottom of verified
  **Consensus (FULL_ARCHIVE)**:
  required_threshold =
    floor(fancy_members / 2) + 1
  Collection window: 10 seconds
  
  **Key Custodian Shortcut**:
  If responder is a pinned
  custodian with valid
  countersignature -> Verified
  immediately (no consensus wait)
end note

@enduml
